records.addlTxt:
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years on count 1 and one (1) year on count 7.
Conditions of probation:
1)	AODA assessment and follow through;
2)	Assessment, treatment, counseling as recommended by the Department's assessment process;
3)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
4)	Maintain absolute sobriety;
5)	Maintain fulltime employment, schooling, treatment, work search or combination;
6)	Have no contact with Walmart.;
7)	Pay restitution of $68.52 to Walmart.  Cash bail applied.  $160.47 balance of cash bail applied to costs;
8)	Pay court costs;
9)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
10)	provide DNA sample.
Minutes.
